sql:
SELECT class_description
FROM travel_classes
WHERE class_id = 0;

SELECT AVG(age) AS average_age
FROM passengers
WHERE pclass = 1;

external_knowledge:
Queenstown is one of the ports where the passengers embarked; 
The query groups the female survivors by ticket class, which is divided into three categories (1st, 2nd, 3rd); 
Each ticket class has a corresponding travel class description (e.g., 1st Class, 2nd Class, 3rd Class) that provides more detailed information.
